@node Overview
@chapter Overview

@samp{org2blog-extras.el} extends @samp{org2blog}, the package that publishes Org mode content to WordPress blogs. The upstream package provides commands for creating, editing, and publishing posts and pages, but its tag handling and confirmation prompts may not suit every workflow.

This package makes two targeted improvements:

@itemize
@item
@strong{Tag migration.} A command to convert standard Org heading tags into the @samp{POST_TAGS} property that @samp{org2blog} uses for WordPress tag assignment (@ref{Tag migration}).
@item
@strong{Smarter confirmation.} Advice that makes the publishing confirmation prompt appear only for new posts (those without a @samp{post-id}), skipping it for updates to already-published content (@ref{Conditional publishing confirmation}).
@end itemize

The package depends on @samp{org2blog}.

